<plot>Chronicle of a rather particular afternoon during which the lives of three people change dramatically: Alex, the husband, goes to his in-laws' to bring home his second wife. Elise, Alex's childhood sweetheart and first wife, accompanies him - as she must, according to tradition. And Josephine, the young bride, leaves her parents to begin a new life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?324862</url></doc>
